            "text": {
                "id": 1452061577,
                "html": "<p>For Helicobacter pylori ERADICATION THERAPY: 1. use a 5-fold higher dose. 2. advise the patient to contact their doctor if symptoms of dyspepsia persist.\nOTHER INDICATIONS: 1. be alert to reduced effectiveness. 2. if necessary, use a 5-fold higher dose. 3. advise the patient to report persisting symptoms of dyspepsia.</p>\n"
